// ============================================================================
// END OF BLUEPRINT
// ============================================================================
// EXPANSION INSTRUCTIONS:
// 1. Replace F1 with F2, F3, F4 to generate additional flows
// 2. Replace 1200 with 1500, 2200, 3000 respectively
// 3. Update BaseNumbers according to corner-specific mapping
// 4. For F2-F4: Replace EndVoltageLimits with:
//    EndVoltageLimits = __shared__::FlowMatrixSingular.CCF_HIGH_SEARCH_VALUE;
// 5. Update all F1 references in parameter names to match corner
//    (e.g., CLR_F1 → CLR_F2, CCF_F1_FREQ → CCF_F2_FREQ)
